  "texts": [
    "There was no significant difference between the groups (p > 0.05), although there was a trend for a larger TFI decrease in the group that received telepsychology (control group: T1-T0 = 11.24, T2-T1 = 3.10; hybrid group: T1-T0 = 19.99, T2-T1 = 0.81).",
    "At post-treatment, 42% of the Tinnibot-only group and 64% of the hybrid-intervention group had a clinically significant improvement (i.e., TFI difference >13).",
    "At follow-up, this was 64% for both groups.",
    "Figure 2 visualizes the change in TFI subscales, showing the smallest change on the auditory subscale, and the largest improvements for the relaxation, emotional, sense of control, and sleep subscales.",
    "Secondary outcome measuresThere was a significant decrease over time in the scores on the PHQ-9 (p < 0.001), but no significant difference was found between the groups (p > 0.05) (Figure 3)."
